pxchat.whiteboard
Class BackgroundFrame

java.lang.Object
  pxchat.net.protocol.frames.Frame
      pxchat.whiteboard.BackgroundFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BackgroundFrame
extends Frame

This frame is used to set a new background. This may either be a new color or an image. The type is specified by the type attribute. The constructor will set the type automatically.
